<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sparkle, sparkle, sparkle!</font>

157
00:05:49,290 --> 00:05:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look so cute! 
I knew it'd look great on you!</font>

158
00:05:52,500 --> 00:05:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can keep that one,</font>

159
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so if you like it, 
try out the other ones, too.</font>

160
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye, now!</font>

161
00:06:00,460 --> 00:06:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Natsuki-kun's just like how he is on TV.</i></font>

162
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank goodness he's nice and friendly.</i></font>

163
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His sense of personal space
 needs work, though.</i></font>

164
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:11,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to working 
with you again today.</font>

165
00:06:14,660 --> 00:06:15,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good evening...</font>

166
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Gloomyhara-san?!</font>

167
00:06:26,610 --> 00:06:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm sorry. I was just surprised.</font>

168
00:06:30,830 --> 00:06:32,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was the lip tint weird?!</i></font>

169
00:06:32,760 --> 00:06:38,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right. No way a hardcore fan with zero sex
 appeal would look good with makeup on.</i></font>

170
00:06:46,590 --> 00:06:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's avoiding me so hard.</i></font>

171
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if he thinks I put on makeup 
just to get his attention?!</i></font>

172
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tamon-kun...</font>

173
00:06:55,770 --> 00:06:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Okay, yeah. 
Marry me, please, please, please,</font>

174
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}please, please, please, please...</font>

175
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm disappointed in you.</font>

176
00:07:01,130 --> 00:07:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}please, please, please, please...</font>

177
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just told him that 
I'm no more than his housekeeper.</i></font>

178
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't want him thinking I'm getting
 my priorities mixed up after all!</i></font>

179
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me!</font>

180
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stay away from me!</font>

181
00:07:19,570 --> 00:07:20,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean...</i></font>

182
00:07:21,170 --> 00:07:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>maybe it's better he keeps his distance
 rather than get awkwardly clingy.</i></font>

183
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gloomyhara-san doesn't
 understand the risks sometimes.</i></font>

184
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... I want to be something to you, too.</font>

185
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Please stop! Don't look at me!</font>

186
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got the wrong idea, 
Gloomyhara-san!</font>

187
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't trying to get your attention 
or anything with this lip tint!</font>

188
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not trying to get you to like me, 
but it hurts to have you dislike me...</font>

189
00:07:57,330 --> 00:07:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I realized that just now!</font>

190
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-There's no way 
I could ever dislike you.</font>

191
00:08:11,690 --> 00:08:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your lips... were so shiny...</font>

192
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:15,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

193
00:08:15,770 --> 00:08:19,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You looked like a mature woman, 
so I got nervous...</font>

194
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You've made the heads of countless 
mature women explode.</i></font>

195
00:08:21,570 --> 00:08:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What are you even saying?</i></font>

196
00:08:22,730 --> 00:08:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... so the lip tint is weird, right?</font>

197
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? It looks really good on you.</font>

198
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh? Huh? Huh? Huh?</font>

199
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="10"><b><font color="#393733">Huh?</font></b></font></font>

200
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="26"><b><font color="#805857">Huh?</font></b></font></font>

201
00:08:30,530 --> 00:08:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="26"><b><font color="#805857">Huh?</font></b></font></font>

202
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="26"><b><font color="#f09296">Huh?</font></b></font></font>

203
00:08:31,580 --> 00:08:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

204
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="26"><b><font color="#e63eaa">Huh</font></b></font></font>

205
00:08:31,780 --> 00:08:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="26"><b><font color="#e63eaa">Huh</font></b></font></font>

206
00:08:32,370 --> 00:08:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this on purpose or 
does he not even realize it?</i></font>

207
00:08:34,470 --> 00:08:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... but I think I'm getting used to it.</font>

208
00:08:38,730 --> 00:08:42,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I coincidentally ran into Natsuki-kun 
at the drugstore earlier,</font>

209
00:08:42,140 --> 00:08:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he put this on me for some reason.</font>

210
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun should be busy today, though.</font>

211
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

212
00:08:47,790 --> 00:08:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You might know this already,</font>

213
00:08:49,610 --> 00:08:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but some of F/ACE's songs 
are written by Natsuki-kun.</font>

214
00:08:53,690 --> 00:08:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And tomorrow's the deadline 
for a new song.</font>

215
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was supposed to be holed up 
in his apartment today.</font>

216
00:08:59,180 --> 00:09:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But I just...</font>

217
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, have you seen Natsuki?</font>

218
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keito-kun.</font>

219
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Earlier, outside.</font>

220
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. Damn it. He ran away again.</font>

221
00:09:08,150 --> 00:09:08,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

222
00:09:09,500 --> 00:09:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He skips out on rehearsals, 
doesn't finish his work,</font>

223
00:09:13,660 --> 00:09:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and doesn't pay people back!</font>

224
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't keep getting away with this!</font>

225
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two look for him, too!</font>

226
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find him and drag his ass back here!</font>

227
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir!</font>

228
00:09:27,990 --> 00:09:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, my head is killin' me.</font>

229
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I drank too much last night.</font>

230
00:09:36,670 --> 00:09:39,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't wanna work.</font>

231
00:09:40,900 --> 00:09:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Big winner!</i></font>

232
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We wandered around the city at night 
trying to find Natsuki-kun.</i></font>

233
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

234
00:10:00,490 --> 00:10:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you find him?!</font>

235
00:10:01,420 --> 00:10:02,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He wasn't over here.</font>

236
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch...</font>

237
00:10:05,830 --> 00:10:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found Natsuki-kun.</font>

238
00:10:09,230 --> 00:10:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When we finally found him...</i></font>

239
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um...</i></font>

240
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is this? More importantly...</i></font>

241
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His room's so messy.</i></font>

242
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough is enough, Natsuki.</font>

243
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh?! Natsuki-kun?!</i></font>

244
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tee-hee!</font>

245
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sparkle!</font>

246
00:10:33,610 --> 00:10:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When I met him at the drugstore,</i></font>

247
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:38,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm fairly certain his eyes 
were at least twice as big!</i></font>

248
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:42,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell do I gotta 
write the songs anyway?</font>

249
00:10:42,340 --> 00:10:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd be better off gettin'
 some pro to do it. This sucks.</font>

250
00:10:45,210 --> 00:10:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't drink alcohol 
when I'm trying to lecture you!</font>

251
00:10:47,930 --> 00:10:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-san sees your talent—</font>

252
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She just doesn't have
 the budget to oursource.</font>

253
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shameless, I tell ya.</font>

254
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just shut up and get to work!</font>

255
00:10:59,850 --> 00:11:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. I don't like you.</font>

256
00:11:04,650 --> 00:11:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that how you talk to someone 
who lent you money?!</font>

257
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:08,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get to work, you stupid smoking addict!</font>

258
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry you had to see that.</font>

259
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm honestly used to it.</font>

260
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:20,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So even Natsuki-kun did
 have a B-side after all.</i></font>

261
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun...</font>

262
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just a slightly heavy smoker 
who loves alcohol and pachinko.</font>

263
00:11:26,420 --> 00:11:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not a bad person...</font>

264
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think. I'm sure of it.</font>

265
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, now I'm worried.</i></font>

266
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry that you ended up getting 
caught up in our group troubles again.</font>

267
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't worry about it. 
But is everything okay?</font>

268
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we got you involved, 
I'll explain the situation.</font>

269
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This could happen again, after all.</font>

270
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Situation?</font>

271
00:11:45,390 --> 00:11:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see, we're getting our own 
flagship show next year and...</font>

272
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keito-kun!</font>

273
00:11:52,690 --> 00:11:59,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="16"><b><font size="20"><font color="#323232">Awawawawawawawawawa</font></font></b></font></font>

274
00:11:52,690 --> 00:11:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san jumped for joy so hard 
that she went through the ceiling!</font>

275
00:11:56,990 --> 00:11:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. what do I do?! What do I do?!</font>

276
00:12:00,050 --> 00:12:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you hurt?</font>

277
00:12:01,860 --> 00:12:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm fine.</font>

278
00:12:03,290 --> 00:12:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I continue?</font>

279
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

280
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki's supposed to write 
the theme song for that show.</font>

281
00:12:10,010 --> 00:12:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we get to hear another 
song Natsuki-kun wrote!</font>

282
00:12:12,560 --> 00:12:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Natsuki-kun isn't motivated at all.</font>

283
00:12:15,410 --> 00:12:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

284
00:12:16,090 --> 00:12:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He usually never shows up when 
we rehearse on our own either...</font>

285
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:22,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we've all been worried about
 his <i>total</i> lack of motivation lately.</font>

286
00:12:23,350 --> 00:12:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our first flagship show...</font>

287
00:12:25,130 --> 00:12:29,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the E/YES have been waiting for this, 
so we want to do our best.</font>

288
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:32,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But with Natsuki-kun being 
in the funk that he's in...</font>

289
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:37,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usually, such a big gap in drive
 among members wouldn't be tolerated,</font>

290
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he's always been hard to deal with.</font>

291
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

292
00:12:42,570 --> 00:12:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to use the john.</font>

293
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tch. Fine.</font>

294
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-He's naked!</font>

295
00:12:54,490 --> 00:12:55,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My eyes!</font>

296
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put on some damn clothes.</font>

297
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, there ain't any A/C in that room.</font>

298
00:13:02,340 --> 00:13:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then go to the bathroom already!</font>

299
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you thinkin' 
that my face looks different?</font>

300
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ack!</i></font>

301
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I, um...</font>

302
00:13:11,270 --> 00:13:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I go like this and...</font>

303
00:13:13,780 --> 00:13:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-dah!</font>

304
00:13:15,070 --> 00:13:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

305
00:13:16,250 --> 00:13:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, yeah. It ain't no plastic surgery.</font>

306
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just don't do it outside work
'cause it wears my eyes out.</font>

307
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's impressive.</font>

308
00:13:23,550 --> 00:13:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'mma go take that piss now.</font>

309
00:13:24,830 --> 00:13:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't say "piss".</font>

310
00:13:27,460 --> 00:13:28,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki-kun.</font>

311
00:13:29,660 --> 00:13:30,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

312
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um, it's nothing...</font>

313
00:13:34,380 --> 00:13:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever.</font>

314
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Another problem with 
F/ACE not getting along?</i></font>

315
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:44,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24" color="#c3c7c4"><b>{\an8}Tokyo Municipal Hanagatani High School</b></font>

316
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:44,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, here's the big announcement!</font>

317
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:47,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The lottery results for what Class 2-A 
will do at the cultural fair is...</font>

318
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="14"><font color="#323232">Cultural Fair Project Application</font></font></font>

319
00:13:47,350 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="24"><font color="#323232">Food Stall</font></font></font>

320
00:13:48,340 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a food stall!</font>

321
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:51,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweet!</font>

322
00:13:51,530 --> 00:13:52,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

323
00:13:52,460 --> 00:13:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So today, we'd like to come up with 
menu ideas and decide everyone's roles.</font>

324
00:13:57,220 --> 00:14:00,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all do the cooking! 
Utage's really good at cooking.</font>

325
00:14:00,090 --> 00:14:02,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Totally. Let's sign up 
for the kitchen team.</font>

326
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey!</font>

327
00:14:03,590 --> 00:14:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, we'll have you in charge 
of the kitchen, Kinoshita-san.</font>

328
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kinoshita will get it done.</font>

329
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Me?!</font>

330
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do our best together.</font>

331
00:14:08,530 --> 00:14:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}She's too perfect!</font>

332
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never taken on a 
leadership position in my life.</i></font>

333
00:14:14,490 --> 00:14:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this going to work?</i></font>

334
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Before I met Tamon-kun, 
I was just living the plain life.</i></font>

335
00:14:20,210 --> 00:14:23,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But since I've been chosen, 
I need to do my best.</i></font>

336
00:14:23,050 --> 00:14:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I'm the leader!</i></font>

337
00:14:24,140 --> 00:14:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kinoshita-san!</font>

338
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seemed a bit down.</font>

339
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:33,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Inoue-sensei...</font>

340
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their new official group shot didn't 
capture Natsuki's good looks at all,</font>

341
00:14:36,610 --> 00:14:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I'm devastated.</font>

342
00:14:39,090 --> 00:14:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just wondering what to do for
 the food stall at the cultural festival.</font>

343
00:14:43,450 --> 00:14:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I see. Hm...</font>

344
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:49,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! This is totally cliché, 
but how about takoyaki?</font>

345
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a great idea. 
I'm gonna jot that down.</font>

346
00:14:51,370 --> 00:14:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, my family runs a takoyaki place.</font>

347
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:58,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our best seller was the cheese yaki. 
We put cheese in instead of octopus.</font>

348
00:14:56,480 --> 00:14:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh?</font>

349
00:14:58,920 --> 00:15:02,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that even takoyaki anymore? 
Though it sounds delicious.</font>

350
00:15:03,200 --> 00:15:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My parents put it on the menu 
for a friend of mine who was broke.</font>

351
00:15:08,220 --> 00:15:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But in the end, all the students
in the neighborhood loved it.</font>

352
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:17,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's cheap to make, and cheese 
does go with everything.</font>

353
00:15:17,470 --> 00:15:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, so I definitely recommend it.</font>

354
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't half-ass this.</font>

355
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're never motivated, so if you lose 
your talent, what are you left with?</font>

356
00:15:28,830 --> 00:15:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't want to bring down 
F/ACE's value, rewrite this song.</font>

357
00:15:43,830 --> 00:15:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

358
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I got in your line of sight 
without permission.</font>

359
00:15:51,850 --> 00:15:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But is everything okay?</font>

360
00:15:56,230 --> 00:15:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you mean about the new show?</font>

361
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, if I'm not 
able to write the song,</font>

362
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure they'll just hire someone else 
or just use one of our old songs.</font>

363
00:16:04,890 --> 00:16:05,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

364
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our show ain't goin' down 
just because of this, so don't worry.</font>

365
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it...</font>

366
00:16:10,660 --> 00:16:13,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm worried about you, Natsuki-kun.</font>

367
00:16:15,010 --> 00:16:17,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Usually, you can do it all.</font>

368
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:20,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've never had such a hard time
 with anything like this before.</font>

369
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothin'.</font>

370
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just not in the mood.</font>

371
00:16:25,690 --> 00:16:27,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what the show's 
gonna be about, don't ya?</font>

372
00:16:27,850 --> 00:16:31,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Youth! Challenges! 
Movin' people to tears!</font>

373
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:33,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, I don't like any of that stuff.</font>

374
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand that a little.</font>

375
00:16:35,850 --> 00:16:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know...</font>

376
00:16:37,350 --> 00:16:41,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you only ever cared
 about yourself, but...</font>

377
00:16:43,770 --> 00:16:45,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you're payin' attention after all.</font>

378
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, you've changed a bit recently.</font>

379
00:16:48,340 --> 00:16:50,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did somethin' change with yer mindset?</font>

380
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mindset?</font>

381
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there is something...</font>

382
00:16:57,370 --> 00:17:00,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be because of a certain someone.</font>

383
00:17:00,370 --> 00:17:01,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh...</font>

384
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font color="#433d35">Tamon</font></b></font>

385
00:17:01,620 --> 00:17:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry!</font>

386
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not here for me, but I started
 rambling about myself!</font>

387
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure why, but I sorta feel 
a bit more motivated now.</font>

388
00:17:08,510 --> 00:17:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

389
00:17:09,130 --> 00:17:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for carin' 'bout me. 
I'll give it a shot.</font>

390
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:16,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, yes...</font>

391
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:18,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, he'll give it a shot.</font>

392
00:17:18,620 --> 00:17:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? That's great!</font>

393
00:17:30,610 --> 00:17:31,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san.</font>

394
00:17:31,850 --> 00:17:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

395
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About what you said the other day...</font>

396
00:17:36,210 --> 00:17:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About how it'd hurt if I disliked you...</font>

397
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly did you mean by that?</font>

398
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:43,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's exactly how it sounds!</font>

399
00:17:43,900 --> 00:17:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody wants to be disliked
 or be seen as a disappointment!</font>

400
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:48,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just general human nature!</font>

401
00:17:48,980 --> 00:17:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, look at the time! 
I'm going to clean the bathtub!</font>

402
00:17:57,520 --> 00:18:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In truth... It's not just 
general human nature.</i></font>

403
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, I didn't just want 
Gloomyhara-san to not hate me...</i></font>

404
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I actually wanted him 
to genuinely like me.</i></font>

405
00:18:08,610 --> 00:18:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a very dangerous train of thought!
 I must kill it before it takes root!</i></font>

406
00:18:15,450 --> 00:18:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-sa...aaaaaaaah!</font>

407
00:18:17,870 --> 00:18:21,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sorry! How could I do this 
to a national treasure?!</font>

408
00:18:26,750 --> 00:18:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't change the subject.</font>

409
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know what I heard.</font>

410
00:18:32,180 --> 00:18:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What could you 
possibly be talking about?</font>

411
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:38,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say that line again.</font>

412
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My ear! Oh my god, my ear!</i></font>

413
00:18:40,860 --> 00:18:42,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am meant to revere you, Tamon-kun!</font>

414
00:18:42,720 --> 00:18:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can never blaspheme you
 with my true thoughts again!</font>

415
00:18:44,890 --> 00:18:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That goes against my dignity!</font>

416
00:18:46,560 --> 00:18:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather bite my tongue and die 
than say something like that again.</font>

417
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's embarrassing just remembering it, 
 so please stop.</font>

418
00:19:00,970 --> 00:19:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it made me really happy.</font>

419
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You finally let go of your reasoning
 and told me how you really feel.</font>

420
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that's exactly why I shouldn't!</i></font>

421
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hear it again.</font>

422
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-As I said, I'd rather 
bite my tongue and die</font>

423
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:20,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">than say something like that again!</font>

424
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, Kinoshita-san...</font>

425
00:19:24,530 --> 00:19:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is...</i></font>

426
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you say something like that... 
just to play with my heart?</font>

427
00:19:30,780 --> 00:19:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His dark side?!</i></font>

428
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to hear that again.</font>

429
00:19:37,430 --> 00:19:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or...</font>

430
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you not die 
for a piece of trash like me?</font>

431
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Utage Kinoshita. Dead at six****.</font>

432
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fafafa"><font color="#000000">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font></font>

433
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font color="#121f2d"><font color="#000000">Utage
Kinoshita</font></font></b></font>

434
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#fafafa"><font color="#000000">m 0 0 l 230 0 l 230 215 l 0 215</font></font></font>

435
00:19:53,050 --> 00:19:55,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font color="#121f2d"><font color="#000000">Dead at</font></font></b></font>

436
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

437
00:19:58,470 --> 00:20:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki disappeared again?!</font>

438
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:03,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find him immediately and bring him back!</font>

439
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yum!</font>

440
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone loves mochi and cheese!</font>

441
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've gotta thank Assu.</font>

442
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}She even lent us a takoyaki maker.</font>

443
00:20:09,530 --> 00:20:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't really understand myself.</i></font>

444
00:20:10,840 --> 00:20:11,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}And gave us recipe advice.</font>

445
00:20:12,860 --> 00:20:15,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just want Tamon to live 
a healthy and happy life.</i></font>

446
00:20:15,900 --> 00:20:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was just content with 
cheering him on from the shadows.</i></font>

447
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But there's something else inside me 
now that wasn't there before.</i></font>

448
00:20:20,380 --> 00:20:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Let's let Assu try them out, too.</font>

449
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:23,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Right, Utage?</font>

450
00:20:23,810 --> 00:20:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's for sure.</i></font>

451
00:20:24,190 --> 00:20:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hello? Utage?</font>

452
00:20:25,860 --> 00:20:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's for sure, but...</i></font>

453
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:28,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you listening?</font>

454
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop fantasizing while you're eating!</font>

455
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm listening! I'm totally listening!</font>

456
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, right? I'll go get her!</font>

457
00:20:40,020 --> 00:20:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it! Come back here!</font>

458
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

459
00:20:46,100 --> 00:20:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give yourself up, you creeper!</font>

460
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei! Are you okay?!</font>

461
00:20:57,530 --> 00:21:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kinoshita-san! Could you call 110?</font>

462
00:20:57,890 --> 00:21:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, wait a sec! Listen to me!</font>

463
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I captured him without thinking.</font>

464
00:21:02,570 --> 00:21:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So OP.</i></font>

465
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, damn it!</font>

466
00:21:05,600 --> 00:21:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's me, Asuka!</font>

467
00:21:08,450 --> 00:21:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natsuki?!</font>

468
00:21:09,930 --> 00:21:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on?! 
Did he just call her "Asuka"?!</i></font>

469
00:21:16,900 --> 00:21:20,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Do you two know each other?</font>

470
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:23,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, sorta...</font>

471
00:21:23,100 --> 00:21:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we don't.</font>

472
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:25,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

473
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen this unfamiliar 
person ever in my life.</font>

474
00:21:27,650 --> 00:21:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, all of Gen Z knows about F/ACE.</font>

475
00:21:31,170 --> 00:21:32,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope, never heard of them.</font>

476
00:21:32,900 --> 00:21:35,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I dropped my smartphone 
into a lake ten years ago.</font>

477
00:21:33,600 --> 00:21:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if this is 
the first time they've met...</i></font>

478
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}At least put some effort into those lies.</font>

479
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Isn't Sensei Natsuki-kun's fan?</i></font>

480
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welp, gotta get back to work.</font>

481
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, Kinoshita-san, I'mma head back.</font>

482
00:21:42,700 --> 00:21:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

483
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:44,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try a little harder!</font>

484
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:48,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure you wanna be a teacher who leaves 
her student with a supposed creeper?!</font>

485
00:21:48,220 --> 00:21:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Asuka!</font>

486
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you two know each other... right?</font>

487
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's one way to put it.</font>

488
00:22:04,550 --> 00:22:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's my ex-girlfriend.</font>

489
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:09,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex-girlfriend...?</i></font>

490
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex-girlfriend...</i></font>

491
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="10"><b><font color="#eb44cb">Ex-girlfriend</font></b></font></font>

492
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ex-girlfriend?!</i></font>

493
00:22:16,110 --> 00:22:21,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="TimesNewRoman">\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hTranslation:
\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hSubtitle Timing:
Editing and Typesetting:</font></font></font>

