501
00:22:47,760 --> 00:22:52,640
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>When I look back, 
you've always been by my side</i></font>

502
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:57,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Teaching me what "warmth" 
and "happiness" feel like</i></font>

503
00:22:57,560 --> 00:23:00,350
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>A speedboat sails across the endless skies</i></font>

504
00:23:00,350 --> 00:23:02,900
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>An unwavering course, 
a straight shot down the middle</i></font>

505
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:05,530
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>An unbreakable red balloon 
found nowhere else</i></font>

506
00:23:05,530 --> 00:23:08,780
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Is this "fate"? Or just a "coincidence"?</i></font>

507
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:13,870
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Like a wilted flower coming back to life</i></font>

508
00:23:13,870 --> 00:23:16,410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>A light that shines</i></font>

509
00:23:16,410 --> 00:23:19,410
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Through the impossibly dark night</i></font>

510
00:23:19,410 --> 00:23:20,710
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>(Light of your soul)</i></font>

511
00:23:20,710 --> 00:23:22,080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>I wanted to grasp it</i></font>

512
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:23,380
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>(I love you so)</i></font>

513
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:24,420
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>So I strived for it</i></font>

514
00:23:24,420 --> 00:23:27,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Wanna keep going, wanna keep growing</i></font>

515
00:23:27,130 --> 00:23:30,930
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#cda710"><i>Bringing our flowers and dreams 
